\"a sampling\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous feature stories\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"Noon ET\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"Carillo\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"her 22ndconsecutive year\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"an analyst\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed doubles title\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1977 French Open\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carillo: \\\"When you cover as many Olympics as I have you inevitably come to think you know how to judge every sport.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Carillo\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"as many Olympics\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"every sport\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Does not matter that you have never tried most of them, especially all those crazy winter events.\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Does not matter that you only watch them for a few days every four years.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Does that stop you from declaring that it was the luger's blunder on turn 27 that cost him the gold?\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the luger's blunder\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hell, no.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hell\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That the forward lean on that last ski jump was premature?\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the forward lean\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"that last ski jump\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That the fall lines in the Nordic combined must be obeyed!\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fall lines\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is it any wonder that by the end of it all when you order coffee you find yourself saying, 'Triple lutz salchow twizzle.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any wonder\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"coffee\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"Triple lutz salchow twizzle\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With oat milk.'\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"oat milk\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It sucks you in, the weeks of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weeks\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if you are as lucky as I am, every morning you text your two great friends, Andrea and Jimmy.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your two great friends\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"Andrea\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"Jimmy\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You write, 'Heading down to breakfast.'\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breakfast\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And they come.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joyce works her 17thOlympics and 13thwith NBC in Paris, reporting from the diving competition as well as serving as a sportsdesk reporter.Next month, Joyce will serve as a reporter at the U.S. Olympic Team Trials-Diving in Knoxville (June 17-23 on NBC, Peacock and USA Network).\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\", \"score\": 0.9999975940001445, \"rank\": 2.406005774521616e-06, \"text\": \"Joyce\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\"}, {\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999124454889715, \"rank\": 8.394545699478854e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.194398440334839e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\", \"score\": 0.9999975940001445, \"rank\": 2.406005774521616e-06, \"text\": \"Joyce\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Joyce\"}, {\"begin\": 2623, \"end\": 2632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knoxville_College\", \"score\": 0.9846086504405455, \"rank\": 0.01563194630901044, \"text\": \"Knoxville\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knoxville_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knoxville_College\"}, {\"begin\": 2648, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999124454889715, \"rank\": 8.394545699478854e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her 17thOlympics\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"the diving competition\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"a sportsdesk reporter\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"a reporter\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Olympic Team Trials-Diving\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"Peacock\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"USA Network\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joyce:\\\"It's always so incredible to be surrounded by the passion and determination of the athletes...many of whom train their whole lives in relative obscurity for just one moment in the spotlight.\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Joyce:\\\"It\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"the passion\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2744}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"their whole lives\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"relative obscurity\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"just one moment\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond that, I love the spirit of generosity at the games.\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the spirit\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"generosity\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No matter what is going on in the world, the Olympics makes us all feel like we are part of one community...a constant reminder that we are more alike than we are different.\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"one community\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"a constant reminder\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To share that with my co-workers is a true gift.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my co\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"a true gift\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years I was incredibly lucky to witness Simone Biles make history countless times.\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3209, \"end\": 3221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But my favorite wasn't a gold medal performance.\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my favorite\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3267}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal performance\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, after withdrawing from the competition, Simone made a remarkable comeback on the last day for the balance beam final.\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3304, \"end\": 3309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"s